lobbying_activities: [{'general_issue_code': 'NAT', 'general_issue_code_display': 'Natural Resources', 'description': "Velta owns the Likarivske and Byrzulivske deposits of ilmenite in Ukraine. For the last nine years, the latter has been serving as the basis of a mining and processing complex that extracts and processes titanium ore. Velta holds 2 percent of the global market for titanium raw materials. Yorktown Solutions will seek to draw attention to the dangers of the continued reliance of the United States and its allies on titanium from strategic competitors, and the ability of Ukraine, working in partnership with the U.S. private and public sectors, to meet many of their needs.
